segments.text: Everybody has a turn back moment. You have a moment where you could go forward
or you can give up. But the thing you have to keep in mind before you give up
is that if you give up, the guarantee is it will never happen. That's the guarantee
of quitting. That it will never happen no way under the sun. The only way the
possibility remains that it can happen is if you never give up no matter what.
